            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Laurenti </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Licinio <expan><abbr>Fab</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> Iuliano <lb n="2"/>equiti Romano <lb n="3"/>patrono et curatori <lb n="4"/>rei <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublicae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Forocl</abbr><ex>odiensium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecturae</ex></expan> Claudiae <lb n="5"/>Laurenti Lavinati <expan><abbr>aed</abbr><ex>ili</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>et praetore <note>sic</note> urbis Lavin<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied> <lb n="7"/>sacerdoti Martis Gr<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>adiv</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>cur</abbr><ex>atori</ex></expan> viae Curtiae p<supplied reason="lost">atro</supplied><lb break="no" n="9"/>no coloniae Car<supplied reason="lost">siolano</supplied><lb break="no" n="10"/>rum <lb n="11"/><supplied reason="lost">de</supplied>curiones <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">populusque</supplied> <lb n="12"/><supplied reason="lost">Foroclodiensium<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> Severo Alexandro <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> III et <lb n="2"/>Cassio Dione II co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> curantibus <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Cestio Arreuctemon<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Iulio Sabiniano
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der Basisoberseite Verdübelungsspuren der Statue. Z. 1 steht auf der corona; Z. 13 - 17 stehen auf der linken Nebenseite, davon Z. 13 u. 14 auf der corona. Auf der linken Nebenseite befindet sich außerdem eine patera, auf der rechten Nebenseite ein guttus im Relief. (B): AE 1979: Z. 10/11: Zeilentrenner nicht angegeben.</p>
            </div>
